1,First run npm install tailwindcss        
         

2.Then run npx tailwindcss init -p 

3.Then in webpack.config.js just copy and paste
Laravel 8 does not come witha default app.scss file so we have to create a default app.scss file 
const mix = require('laravel-mix');
const tailwindcss = require('tailwindcss');
 
mix.js('resources/js/app.js', 'public/js')
    .sass('resources/css/app.scss', 'public/css')
    .options({
        processCssUrls: false,
        postCss: [tailwindcss('./tailwind.config.js')],
    });
 

After doing this run npm run dev and npm run watch
3. Link your app.css file must have all tailwind classes
4. Then you link your css file to blade 
 <link href="{{ mix('css/app.css') }}" rel="stylesheet">

